issues with the above output and your sources.list file:

1.  "http://cran.rstudio.com/bin/linux/ubuntu bionic/" is incorrect.
It should be "http://cran.rstudio.com/bin/linux/ubuntu bionic-cran35/"
2.  You are mixing Bionic and Cosmic, which we do not recommend.

Michael

